        <h2> About Us</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to Automatic Presentation Evaluation (APE) - your revolutionary solution for smart education assessment. At APE, we're a team of five dedicated individuals passionate about enhancing the educational experience through cutting-edge technology.

            <pre>





            </pre>
            Our mission is to streamline the evaluation process for student presentations, empowering educators and students alike. By harnessing the power of machine learning algorithms, we've developed a comprehensive system that assesses various aspects of a presentation, including confidence, expression, and sentiment analysis.
            <pre>





            </pre>
            With APE, teachers can now efficiently manage student scores while ensuring unbiased and industry-standard evaluations. Our innovative approach not only saves time but also enhances the learning experience, allowing students to receive constructive feedback tailored to their individual needs.
            <pre>




            </pre>
            Video applications present common but difficult challenges that require flexible analysis and processing functionality. Using MATLAB and Simulink products, you can develop solutions to common video processing challenges such as video stabilization, video mosaicking, target detection, and tracking.
            <pre>



            

            </pre>
            Join us on this journey to revolutionize the education system and take it a step forward with Automatic Presentation Evaluation. Let's shape the future of education together.<br><br>
